description: Found with most of its organs intact, the rhino is thought to have lived more than 20,000 years ago.
title: Woolly rhino from Ice Age unearthed in Russian Arctic
title_page: Woolly rhino from Ice Age unearthed in Russian Arctic - BBC News
maintext: They are waiting for ice roads to form so they can take the remains to the city of Yakutsk, where scientists will take samples and carry out radiocarbon analyses.
